OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780427467
OL,3,C#8m lost to social housing fraud in
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland
OL,6,FSocial housing fraud cost the public
OL,7,Fpurse in Northern Ireland around #8
OL,8,Fmillion in 2024/25, according to a new
OL,9,Freport.
OL,11,FThe Northern Ireland Audit Office
OL,12,F(NIAO) has said each case of social
OL,13,Fhousing fraud costs more than #28,000
OL,14,Fin a report warning that the full
OL,15,Fextent of the issue is still unknown.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
