OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780427467
OL,3,C#8m lost to social housing fraud in
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland
OL,6,FThe report by Comptroller and Auditor
OL,7,FGeneral Dorinnia Carville notes that
OL,8,Fdemand for social housing has reached
OL,9,Funprecedented levels and Northern
OL,10,FIreland still lacks an evidence-based
OL,11,Festimate of the scale of tenancy
OL,12,Ffraud, despite this being recommended
OL,13,Fmore than a decade ago.
OL,15,FThere are approximately 134,000 social
OL,16,Fhomes in Northern Ireland, most of
OL,17,Fwhich are managed by the Northern
OL,18,FIreland Housing Executive (NIHE), with
OL,19,Fthe remainder managed by registered
OL,20,Fhousing associations (RHAs).
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780427467
OL,3,C#8m lost to social housing fraud in
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland
OL,6,FEstimates in England suggest that up
OL,7,Fto one in 30 social homes may be
OL,8,Faffected and were this rate to be
OL,9,Fapplied locally, it would mean as many
OL,10,Fas 4,000 properties in Northern
OL,11,FIreland could be subject to some form
OL,12,Fof tenancy fraud or misuse.
OL,14,FBy comparison, in 2024-25, a total of
OL,15,F284 social houses were recovered in
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland as a result of
OL,17,Ftenancy fraud and misuse.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780427467
OL,3,C#8m lost to social housing fraud in
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland
OL,6,FThe NIAO says these cases incur a
OL,7,Ffinancial cost to the local economy
OL,8,F(for example, investigation costs,
OL,9,Flegal costs and temporary
OL,10,Faccommodation costs), with latest
OL,11,Festimates putting the cost of each
OL,12,Fcase at #28,450.
OL,14,FFor the 284 houses identified, this
OL,15,Fequates to a total cost to the public
OL,16,Fpurse of approximately #8 million in
OL,17,F2024-25.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780427467
OL,3,C#8m lost to social housing fraud in
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland
OL,6,FThe report does acknowledge progress
OL,7,Fmade by the Department for Communities
OL,8,Fand NIHE to develop measures for
OL,9,Ftackling tenancy fraud and misuse.
OL,11,FMs Carville said every "case of
OL,12,Ftenancy fraud and misuse denies a
OL,13,Fsocial home to someone in need at a
OL,14,Ftime when housing waiting lists are at
OL,15,Frecord highs.
OL,17,F"There is also a significant financial
OL,18,Fcost, with a direct cost of #8 million
OL,19,Fin 24-25.
OL,26,@sD@XOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780427467
OL,3,C#8m lost to social housing fraud in
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland
OL,6,F"In addition, my report last year on
OL,7,Fhomelessness in Northern Ireland
OL,8,Fhighlighted that a lack of social
OL,9,Fhousing is resulting in an increasing
OL,10,Fand costly reliance on temporary
OL,11,Faccommodation, with expenditure
OL,12,Fcontinuing to rise to over #40 million
OL,13,Fin 2025.
OL,15,F"Tackling this issue effectively
OL,16,Fstarts with understanding the scale of
OL,17,Fthe problem, which has been inhibited
OL,18,Fby an unco-ordinated and inconsistent
OL,19,Fapproach to recording and reporting
OL,20,Fdata.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1780427467
OL,3,C#8m lost to social housing fraud in
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland
OL,6,F"I have therefore recommended that the
OL,7,Fdepartment establish an evidence-based
OL,8,Fbaseline estimate within the next six
OL,9,Fmonths.
OL,11,F"My report also recommends that the
OL,12,Fdepartment makes it a requirement of
OL,13,Fboth the NI Housing Executive and the
OL,14,Fregistered housing associations to
OL,15,Fimplement an annual co-ordinated
OL,16,Fprogramme of tenancy fraud and misuse
OL,17,Faudits, to help ensure a more
OL,18,Fstrategic and joined-up approach
OL,19,Facross the social housing sector."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU{D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/8
